    "CSPE can predict category-sentiment pairs regardless of whether the aspect is explicitly mentioned or implicit in the sentence (Bu et al. 2021).",
    "CSPE uses a pipeline approach.",
    "However, detecting a subset of aspect categories is challenging, and errors in the first step can impact performance.",
    "The relationship between the two steps is essential but often ignored (Hu et al. 2019b).",
    "Multi-task learning benefits both tasks (Hu et al. 2019b; Ma et al. 2018; Dai et al. 2020)."
